<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 mb-4">
    <h4 class="text-primary">
      <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2"></i>{{data.RegionName}}
      <small class="text-muted">({{data.Year}})</small>
    </h4>
    <hr />
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card bg-danger text-white h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-white-50">Inequality Gap</h6>
        <h2 class="card-title display-4 fw-bold">{{formatDecimal
            data.TheInequalityGap
            2
          }}</h2>
        <p class="card-text">years</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card bg-success text-white h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-white-50">Best (Highest)</h6>
        <h2 class="card-title display-4 fw-bold">{{formatDecimal
            data.BestMetric
            2
          }}</h2>
        <p class="card-text">years</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card bg-warning h-100">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Worst (Lowest)</h6>
        <h2 class="card-title display-4 fw-bold">{{formatDecimal
            data.WorstMetric
            2
          }}</h2>
        <p class="card-text">years</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 mt-4">
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <i class="bi bi-lightbulb me-2"></i>
      <strong>Interpretation:</strong>
      The inequality gap of
      <strong>{{formatDecimal data.TheInequalityGap 2}} years</strong>
      represents the difference in life expectancy between the healthiest and
      least healthy countries within
      {{data.RegionName}}. A larger gap indicates greater health disparity in
      the region.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>